name: CodeGlyphDecoded
summary: Result of decoding a QR or barcode symbol.

properties.name: Qr
properties.summary: Gets the decoded QR result when CodeGlyphX.CodeGlyphDecoded.Kind is CodeGlyphX.CodeGlyphKind.Qr.

properties.name: Barcode
properties.summary: Gets the decoded barcode result when CodeGlyphX.CodeGlyphDecoded.Kind is CodeGlyphX.CodeGlyphKind.Barcode1D.

properties.name: DataMatrixText
properties.summary: Gets the decoded Data Matrix text when CodeGlyphX.CodeGlyphDecoded.Kind is CodeGlyphX.CodeGlyphKind.DataMatrix.

properties.name: Pdf417Text
properties.summary: Gets the decoded PDF417 text when CodeGlyphX.CodeGlyphDecoded.Kind is CodeGlyphX.CodeGlyphKind.Pdf417.

properties.name: Pdf417
properties.summary: Gets the decoded PDF417 payload when CodeGlyphX.CodeGlyphDecoded.Kind is CodeGlyphX.CodeGlyphKind.Pdf417.

properties.name: Pdf417Macro
properties.summary: Gets the Macro PDF417 metadata when present.

properties.name: AztecText
properties.summary: Gets the decoded Aztec text when CodeGlyphX.CodeGlyphDecoded.Kind is CodeGlyphX.CodeGlyphKind.Aztec.

properties.name: Bytes
properties.summary: Gets the decoded payload bytes for QR codes.
